events.title: The National Parks: Wild Spirit Tour
events.location: Phoenix, Arizona, United States Of America
events.description: DOORS: 7PM SHOW: 8PM Please Note: This event is 13+ (Ages 5-12 must be accompanied by a parent/legal guardian. Children 4 and under not admitted.) *BAG POLICY* - Bags up to 12" x 6" x 12" are allowed in the venue (NO BACKPACKS) - All bags will be searched prior to entry - Bags that are not clear will be subject to additional search All support acts are subject to change without notice. Delivery is delayed for this event; tickets will be released 72 hours prior to the show. Purchase of a mezzanine seat includes the following: an event ticket for the show, a private VIP entrance (skip the GA line), a reserved seat on the mezzanine, access to a private bar, and a cocktail server.
